&lt;p&gt;Is it a bug?&lt;/p&gt;
</title><link>https://faq.i3wm.org/question/6569/i3-msg-not-toggling-scratchpad/?comment=6593#comment-6593</link><description>As vandannen said, if the scratchpad window is not focused, it will be focused. It will only be hidden, if it is focused. When you run `i3-msg` from some other window, that window has the focus. If you use this only for testing you can use `sleep 2 ; i3-msg ...` and manually focus the window.</description><pubDate>Wed, 16 Sep 2015 11:17:34 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://faq.i3wm.org/question/6569/i3-msg-not-toggling-scratchpad/?comment=6593#comment-6593</guid></item><item><title>Comment by tigrezno for &lt;p&gt;I'm issuing this:&lt;/p&gt;

