&lt;p&gt;It shows the scratchpad, but when executed again, scratchpad won't hide like with the keybind.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Is it a bug?&lt;/p&gt;
</title><link>https://faq.i3wm.org/question/6569/i3-msg-not-toggling-scratchpad/?comment=6578#comment-6578</link><description>But why the keybind version acts like a toggle, but i3-msg won't?</description><pubDate>Mon, 14 Sep 2015 09:02:58 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://faq.i3wm.org/question/6569/i3-msg-not-toggling-scratchpad/?comment=6578#comment-6578</guid></item><item><title>Comment by vandannen for &lt;p&gt;I'm issuing this:&lt;/p&gt;

