</title><link>https://faq.i3wm.org/question/6569/i3-msg-not-toggling-scratchpad/?comment=6572#comment-6572</link><description>I do not know if that is what you are experiencing, but 'scratchpad show' will only move the currently shown scratchpad window back to scratchpad if it is currently focused, otherwise it will just focus that window.</description><pubDate>Sat, 12 Sep 2015 11:24:02 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://faq.i3wm.org/question/6569/i3-msg-not-toggling-scratchpad/?comment=6572#comment-6572</guid></item><item><title>Comment by tigrezno for &lt;p&gt;I'm issuing this:&lt;/p&gt;

